summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1433, for the improvement of Elmwood Place from 27th Avenue South to Bradner Place, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle by grading and curbing the same, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 15529 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
